This paper is likely to belong to the sub-category of cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it deals with the hyper-parameter search problem in the field of machine learning. Additionally, it may also belong to cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as it specifically focuses on feedforward neural networks. The paper's heuristic approach may also fall under the sub-category of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as it involves optimizing the performance of a learning algorithm. Furthermore, the use of neural networks suggests that the paper may also be relevant to the sub-categories of cs.CV (Computer Vision) and cs.CL (Computation and Language).
